  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/5ebd2e1d74f234d55e9581fde14bf8f5.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy story, puzzles, and battles against monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/18a2fe5fae6f68f90723aad4c49d4e28.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/4cad9d2c15169f6b5ced35e502f1f99f.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/ec6b328220c27edceeb8c2ead7f99d29.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Risa wakes up in a mansion with no memory. There, she meets her family and friends and gradually begins to recover fragments of her past. Along the way, she starts to realize that she is not the same as others...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/324d70d26f219c2df653c0fc0117a4c4.avif?t=1764856832\" width=606 height=307 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/47cc5bc95eb7b6f4a0593ccc54f6fc28.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to open blocked paths or obtain keys that unlock doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/cfd50b0f034f92541e4ed8b9348eea50.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/b688a0c05874f2f673c5a5f3160e0ef0.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/3caa066c406efa14dc9eec754e4b61de.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use weapons to defeat the monsters that stand in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/f204e50444beb78b1dd9f4c9f295dc71.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/45771ad02c9ce72f9726913086b0116b.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/2b16f1a5d2c852727e1d17c44489e61e.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/5ebd2e1d74f234d55e9581fde14bf8f5.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy story, puzzles, and battles against monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/18a2fe5fae6f68f90723aad4c49d4e28.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/4cad9d2c15169f6b5ced35e502f1f99f.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/ec6b328220c27edceeb8c2ead7f99d29.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Risa wakes up in a mansion with no memory. There, she meets her family and friends and gradually begins to recover fragments of her past. Along the way, she starts to realize that she is not the same as others...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/324d70d26f219c2df653c0fc0117a4c4.avif?t=1764856832\" width=606 height=307 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/47cc5bc95eb7b6f4a0593ccc54f6fc28.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to open blocked paths or obtain keys that unlock doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/cfd50b0f034f92541e4ed8b9348eea50.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/b688a0c05874f2f673c5a5f3160e0ef0.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/3caa066c406efa14dc9eec754e4b61de.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1080 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use weapons to defeat the monsters that stand in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/f204e50444beb78b1dd9f4c9f295dc71.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/45771ad02c9ce72f9726913086b0116b.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1792770/extras/2b16f1a5d2c852727e1d17c44489e61e.avif?t=1764856832\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
